question: Which title has a year prior to the other year for the films of Andy Fickman between the one that has an infant and a timepiece on the poster or the one that shows someone in a football uniform?
context: The Game Plan is a 2007 American family comedy film directed by Andy Fickman and written by Nichole Millard, Kathryn Price and Audrey Wells and starring Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson (marking the last film in which Johnson uses his ring name "The Rock" in billing). It follows a professional quarterback who finds out he has an 8-year-old daughter from a previous relationship.
